{"tid":664417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列女歌手為#MeToo發聲 歐洲歌唱大賽奪冠","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:50:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55f0e85a086ad351234d9724c786281bd8aa0ee5","tid":664417,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180513/_2018051320271067491.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180513%2F_2018051320271067491.jpg&h=c383ab9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以色列女歌手巴爾齊萊。新華社</span><br />\n<br />\n以色列女歌手巴爾齊萊 (Netta Barzilai) 以動感歌曲《玩具》(Toy) 為「#MeToo」反性侵運動發聲，結果擊敗其他25名參賽者，在葡萄牙里斯本舉辦的第63屆歐洲歌唱大賽中奪冠。這已是以色列第4度在這項盛事中取勝。<br />\n<br />\n巴爾齊萊奪冠後，在舞台上發表得獎感言時說：「下一屆在耶路撒冷舉行！我很開心，非常感謝。感謝大家支持多元文化。」<br />\n<br />\n《玩具》副歌歌詞為「我不是你的玩具，你這個愚蠢的男孩」，為許多女性的憂慮做了總結，呼應在全球延燒的反性侵和騷擾運動。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的巴爾齊萊，曾任以色列海軍樂團歌手，她以打舌、咯咯叫聲與模仿雞的舞蹈，在歐洲歌唱大賽脫穎而出。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲歌唱大賽原本只是歐洲各國間的國際音樂賽事，但在其他各地引發熱烈迴響下，也陸續將以色列和澳洲納入比賽。估計全球有約二億人收看周六晚轉播的歐洲歌唱大賽。<br />\n<br />\n由於去年葡萄牙歌手索布拉爾 (Salvador Sobral) 以哀傷風格的歌曲《Amar Pelos Dois》奪冠，葡萄牙因此獲得今年的歐洲歌唱大賽主辦權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180513/_2018051320271895943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180513%2F_2018051320271895943.jpg&h=f5ec35dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180513/_2018051320271170077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180513%2F_2018051320271170077.jpg&h=abcd599c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180513/_2018051320271491746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180513%2F_2018051320271491746.jpg&h=89a6c173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/714817-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%A5%B3%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%23MeToo%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2+%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F714817-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%2523MeToo%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2B%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%25AD%258C%25E5%2594%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbhxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7ef9be42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F714817-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%2523MeToo%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%2B%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%25AD%258C%25E5%2594%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2586%25A0&h=5771e1f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/714817-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%A5%B3%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%23MeToo%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2+%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%AD%8C%E5%94%B1%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD%E5%A5%AA%E5%86%A0</a>"},{"pid":"81fcb6687c2755bbda0faa5447f6b87fc332dc0e","tid":664417,"uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"佢應該唔洗擔心被人性侵啩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6410d5186f902c42a9dd6fa6bced27e4940fcc12","tid":664417,"uid":172840,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （以色列版）"},{